frames.caption: A serene waterfall cascades down a rocky cliff, surrounded by lush foliage and a majestic tree with vibrant red leaves. Petals gently float through the air, adding a touch of whimsy to the tranquil scene. In the distance, a flock of birds soars across the sky, enhancing the sense of freedom and peace.
